qas.question: How many UEFA Championship League titles has Barcelona won?
How many UEFA  Cup Winners' Cup wins does Barcelona have?
How many UEFA Super Cup wins does the Barcelona team have?
How many FIFA Club World Cup trophies does football club Barcelona have?

In international club football, Barcelona has won <a0_0>five<a0_0/> UEFA Champions League titles, a record <a1_0>four<a1_0/> UEFA Cup Winners' Cup, a shared record <a2_0>five<a2_0/> UEFA Super Cup, a record three Inter-Cities Fairs Cup and a record <a3_0>three<a3_0/> FIFA Club World Cup trophies. Barcelona was ranked first in the IFFHS Club World Ranking for 1997, 2009, 2011, 2012 and 2015 and currently occupies the second position on the UEFA club rankings. The club has a long-standing rivalry with <a4_0>Real Madrid<a4_0/>; matches between the two teams are referred to as El Clásico.
